Product Name: Unisex Originals CRAIG GREEN KONTUUR I SHOES
Description: Live for the unpredictable. London-born designer Craig Green brings unexpected whimsy and dramatic style to his collaboration with adidas. The Kontuur I shoes blend his signature quilted design with an adidas Kamanda outsole to create an inventive style that's rich in texture.

These slip-on trainers have a sock-like upper with an exaggerated puffer look borrowed from winter wear. The lacing system features a stopper closure on the heel.

Optimized Boost maximizes energy return, and a 3D heel frame gives a locked-down fit for natural heel movement.
